title: The World Of Enochian Magick (Golden Dawn Audios)
description:
An essential reference and study aid for all serious students of magic. Instruction on Enochian, the angelic spiritual language, as it is used to communicate with the spirits as part of the practice of magic and spiritual development.

The CD provides an unparalleled and unique opportunity to hear Dr. Regardie's own voice giving instruction on Enochiana plus a variety of Enochian Keys and Calls.

Included are the original tracks:


   1. The Revealing
   2. Short Enochian Call from the Portal Ritual (Enochian)
   3. Short Enochian Call from the Portal Ritual (English)
   4. Introduction to the Short Enochian Call by Aleister Crowley
   5. Short Enochian Call by Aleister Crowley (Enochian)
   6. Short Enochian Call by Aleister Crowley (English)
   7. Short Enochian Call by Aleister Crowley (vibrated)
   8. The 1st 11 Enochian Keys
   9. The Call of the 39th Aethyr
  10. The Call of the 1st Aethyr  


Plus additional tracks featuring the first 10 calls in both English and Enochian.


Please SEED and ENJOY!


93, 93/93
